Package com.github.nosan.embedded.cassandra.cql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CqlScript
    CQL Script that abstracts from the actual type of underlying resource.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCqlScript
    Convenience base class for CqlScript implementations, pre-implementing CQL scripts parsing.
    ClassLoaderUtils
    Utility class to detect ClassLoader.
    ClassPathCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for class path resources.
    CqlScriptParser
    Utility class for parsing CQL Script into the statements.
    CqlScriptUtils
    Utility class for working with Scripts.
    FileCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for File.
    InputStreamCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for InputStream.
    PathCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for Path.
    StaticCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for a given CQL statements.
    UrlCqlScript
    CqlScript implementation for URL.
